Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:27.59,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more time! I'll reach out{\i}\N{\i1}to you as many times as you need{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.00,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:27.44,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何度でも手を伸ばそう
