Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの風邪だってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, she shouldn't worry us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.74,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう心配かけさせないで欲しいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:47.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すこし…すこしあいつに頼り過ぎていたのかもしれないな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we've been leaning on her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't waste time\Nthinking about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今はそんなことを言っている場合ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Waste time"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save the self-reflection for later.\NWe have to get started now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,反省は後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに取りかかるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.20,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,取りかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The screenings are canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上映会は中止だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Canceled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと残念ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,出来ていないのだから仕方ないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not finished. We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:14.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それに　最初は七人で見なければ意味がないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless if all seven of\Nus aren't at the first viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.78,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,240)}The Neighbors Club movie\Nscreenings have been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:44.93,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうりゃ 掲示板に悪戯しないでくださいって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No messing around with the bulletin board!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasegawa-{\i1}kun{\i0}, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,羽瀬川君じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi, Yusa. I'm not messing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.73,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊佐か　悪戯じゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My club's presentation was canceled,\Nso I'm taking down the posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.26,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部活の出し物が中止になったから　ポスターの回収をしてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これは失礼しました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not the type of\Nperson to pull pranks, Hasegawa-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:04:01.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに羽瀬川君のような人が　迷惑行為などするわけがありませんよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm kind of moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.18,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　ちょっと感動して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually people don't believe me, or\Nthey just run away before I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.91,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもは釈明してもわかってもらえないか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,釈明する前に逃げられるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand you, but\Nclearly you must have a sensitive soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よくわかりませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと羽瀬川君は感情性が豊なのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a perfect boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:22.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがリア充完璧超人柏崎星奈にぴったりのパーフェクトな彼氏さんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to match the inhumanly perfect\Nreal-lifer Kashiwazaki Sena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not her boyfriend!\NWe're just clubmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だから彼氏じゃねえよ　ただの部活仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Clubmates? But Kashiwazaki\NSena isn't in any clubs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:30.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部活仲間　柏崎星奈は部活に入ってなかったはずです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The club started in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,六月から始めたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Neighbors Club"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隣人部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that club.\NWhat do you do in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたことがない名前です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をする部活なのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Excuse me, I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.47,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと　すまん　ちょっと急いでるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for delaying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お引止めしてすみませんでした
