Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうでした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with this club?!\NAll you ever do is play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんですか　この部活は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊んでばっかりじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今はたまたま休憩していただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We just happen to be taking a break right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's no use lying! I've kept\Ntabs on you for some time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.38,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,嘘をついても無駄です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:46.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分はずっとあなた達を監視していたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,監視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got curious about what kind of\Nclub you and Kashiwazaki Sena were in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,羽瀬川君や柏崎星奈が所属している部活が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなのか気になったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:12:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Supposing we {\i1}did{\i} play all\Nthe time, would that be a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:58.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,で　私達がこの部室で遊んでばかりいたとして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.77,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が問題があるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部活にはそれぞれの活動方針がある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Each club has its own activity program.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部外者に口出しされるいわれはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Outsiders have no right to stick their noses in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分は生徒会役員です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am on the student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:11.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会には道を踏み外した生徒を正す義務があります
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Council members have a duty to\Ncorrect students who stray from the path!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんつうか　遊佐は星奈をライバル視してて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yusa thinks of Sena as a rival or\Nsomething. I think that's why she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,多分その流れで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.01,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,っちぇ　肉のせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Meat's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Neighbors Club is\Nofficially recognized by the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隣人部とは学校に認められた部であり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and we abide by its stated aims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,我々はその活動目的に従っている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In compliance with God's instructions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,神の教えに則り
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ学校に通う仲間の良き隣人となり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we become neighbors with our\Nfellow students, deepen that friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,友誼を深めるべく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誠心誠意臨機応変に切磋琢磨する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and, as occasion may require,\Nsincerely work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, what appears\Nto be mere playing around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊んでいるように見えるのは立派な隣人部の活動なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is in fact perfectly legitimate club business!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed she remembers that spiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく覚えてるな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We play video games and read
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームをするのも　読書をするのも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全ては同じ学校に通う仲間の良き隣人となるためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to become good\Nneighbors to our fellow students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You want some too, don't you?\NFun friends. Knowledgeable friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様もほしいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い友達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知識が豊富な友達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends who share your\Ninterests. Dependable friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,趣味が合う友達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りになる友達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:58.70,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We work hard together each day in\Nour quest to be magnificent neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私達はそんな素晴らしい隣人になることを目指し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,日々切磋琢磨しているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:10.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,た　確かに　そうした友人の存在は人生を豊にしてくれると思います
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,T-True, I believe such friends\Nwould enrich a person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't seem to be doing that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　とてもそんなふうには見えませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}your{\i} personal impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは貴様の主観だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the council reject the activities of law-abiding\Nstudents based on personal impressions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会は主観で善良な一般生徒の活動を否定するのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　そこの人とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or {\i1}that{\i} one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あと　あの人とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's right to break school rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,校則違反をするのはよくないと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,School rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,校則違反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,服装です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at their clothes! According\Nto Student Handbook Article 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.61,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒心得五条　服装に関する規定により
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the Rules for Attire, " Students\Nare required to wear their uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本学園の生徒は登校下校及び　校内においては
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,while on campus as well as\Non their way to and from sch..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学園規定の制服を着用することが義務つけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 5 Section 4 stipulates\Nthe exceptions to that rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:44.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,五条四項に制服着用義務の例外が定められている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe club activities\Nare specifically included.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:48.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部活同時もそこに含まれると明記されているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Four... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.34,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,四　四
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But these exceptions are for\Ngym clothes and other uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:56.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　ここで規定されているのは体操着やユニホームのことで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you should fill\Nout the official paperwork
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なら校則改定手続きを取って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the handbook amended to clarify that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.59,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう明記されるよう変えることだな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.92,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くくく　我は人間の定めた法理など縛られぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not bound by human laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それお前は中等部だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle school? What's a middle\Nschool student doing in this club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中等部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中等部の子がどうして部員になっているのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no rule stating that\Nmiddle schoolers can't be club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.45,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中等部の生徒を部員にしてはいけないという規定はない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Outsiders aren't allowed inside\Nschool buildings without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,部外者が許可なく校舎内立ち入ることは禁止されています
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,True, perhaps it is against the\Nrules to allow outsiders into a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:24.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに部外者を入部させるのは校則違反かもしれないな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:25.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But are the middle schoolers "outsiders"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:28.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　中等部の生徒は部外者か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Though in a different school, they are\Nnevertheless students of St. Chronica's Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,中等部とは言え
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,れっきとした聖クロニカ学園所属する学生であり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, is it reasonable to\Ncall our blood relatives "outsiders"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.87,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも部員の血縁者を部外者とするのは無理があるのではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, this chapel\Nmay be on school grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:44.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さらにこの礼拝堂は学園の敷地内に建ってはいるが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is open to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一般開放されている施設でもある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there is no problem\Nwith Hasegawa Kodaka's sister
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:52.22,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よって羽瀬川小鷹の妹が部員としてここにいることに何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,being here as a club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.10,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrrr... Th-This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.17,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えておいてください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! And {\i1}stay{\i} out, student council dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.03,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二度と来るな　生徒会の犬目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversations with\Nstrangers make me nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知らない人間と会話するのは緊張する
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お疲れさん　部長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日こそ観念してもらいます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,またお前か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your confidence is about to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その余裕もここまでです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found a definitive reason why the\NNeighbors Club isn't a legitimate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:39.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,隣人部が正式な部として求められない決定的な理由を見つけました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,More crazy talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,また妄言を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Section 2 of the Rules\Nfor Extracurricular Activities:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学校外の活動に関する規定二項
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"As a rule, classes, clubs, and\Nother activities undertaken in groups
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラスクラブ等の団体での活動については
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:51.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,関係教官の引率がない場合 原則としてこれを認めない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,must be conducted under\Nthe supervision of an instructor"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに部活には顧問が必要ってことだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means clubs\Nhave to have advisors, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And your advisor is the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その顧問が問題なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 78 of the Student Council bylaws
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.41,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,生徒会会則七十八条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,states that "Club advisors must\Nbe faculty or staff of this school"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:03.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブの顧問は本校に勤務する教官または職員であること
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Per Section 2, a sister's\Nrights and responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:08.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,規定二項において　シスターの権利と義務は教官のそれに順ずるものとある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,are equivalent to those of the faculty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.53,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}if{\i} your adviser were a\Nsister, there would be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.80,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに　シスターが顧問なら問題はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Takayama Maria\Nover there is {\i1}not{\i} a sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:17.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが　そこにいる高山マリアさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,シスターではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no "Takayama Maria" on the\Nlist of sisters assigned to this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,学園に派遣されているシスターの名簿に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,「高山マリア」という名前はありません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only her older sister Kate-{\i1}sensei{\i} is listed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.31,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,記載されているのは姉のケイト先生の名前のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, she's just a\Nlittle girl who hangs out in the chapel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:36.71,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり彼女は礼拝堂に出入りしているだけのただの幼女なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だ　だが　創部届けは問題なく受理されたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But the club application was approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Merely a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それはただのミスです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.14,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん　どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something...\NIsn't Maria a sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.90,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,聞きたいことがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアってさ　シスターじゃないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなあっさり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having her act as my assistant,\Npartly to learn about the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:17:00.33,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,社会勉強も兼ねて私の手伝いをさせているのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, if she's at my school,\NI can keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.13,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ学校にいれば私の目もちゃんと届くからね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why does Maria call herself "{\i1}sensei{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアが自分のこと　先生って言ってるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just something she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつが勝手に言ってるだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So why does she wear nun's robes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃなんでシスター服を着てるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,可愛いからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.13,Default - Style 01,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\be5\an8\pos(620,368)\c&HEFECE7&\3c&H594431&}Takayama Kate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.11,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マジでシスターじゃないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she really {\i1}isn't{\i} a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So I'm not a sister after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私はシスターじゃなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I am, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,私って一体何なんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, since you don't have an advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく顧問がいない以上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,正式な部として認められません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be recognized as a legitimate club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不正な手段で作られた部として廃部の処分もあり得るでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As a club formed under false\Npretenses, you could be disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それがいやなら今後はもって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want that, then\Nfrom now on you'd better...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If Maria's an official\Nadvisor, we're good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアが正式な顧問ならいいのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, but... The issue\Nis that she's {\i1}not,{\i} so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.21,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでないから駄目なわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Wait here a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあちょっと待ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コーヒーでも飲むか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry; it's not poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:59.00,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心配すんな　毒なんか入ってないから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I've carelessly missed\Na chance to eliminate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたくしとしたことが　敵を排除する好機を逃してしまいました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminating her really isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.85,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　排除しなくていいから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,待たせたわね　愚民共
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting, commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria's been offered a position\Nas a special part-time instructor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.05,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,マリアが特別非常勤講師に内定したわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a "special part-time instructor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.49,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特別非常勤講師って何なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.32,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先生みたいなものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パパに電話して相談したの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I called Daddy about our little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be a real teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わたし　本当の先生になれるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.48,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うん　どうする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なる　なります
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We'll put in the paperwork, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.23,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あっそう　それじゃ手続きするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yay! Yay! I'm gonna be a real teacher!\N- Daddy? About what we were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:37.87,夏雪日文旁白-ja,,0,0,0,,ふわふわ　わたし本当の先生になるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.69,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ　さっきの件だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yay, yay!\N- Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm. Thanks. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.55,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,宜しくね　じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.52,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなの無茶苦茶です
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The school president made the\Ndecision. Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理事長が決めたのよ　文句ある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あるに決まってます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも今更正式な顧問を立てたところで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And getting a proper advisor {\i1}now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不正な手段で作られた部という事実に変わり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't change the fact that\Nthe club was created on false...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence, mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.08,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,黙りなさい　駄犬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, even if the\Nstudent council calls for our disbandment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.54,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ生徒会が廃部を申し立てようが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get that proposal canned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り潰すことも出来るの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got us an advisor for you so\Nthat {\i1}you{\i} don't look like a fool later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.28,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの顔を潰さないよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.06,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと顧問を立ててあげたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝しなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの　自分は認めません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, mongrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.75,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よく聞きなさい　駄犬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This club belongs to me.\NIf you keep barking on my turf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この部はあたしのものなの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:17.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もしあたしの庭でこれ以上うるさく吠えるようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.35,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,捻り潰すわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.89,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,退学にでもしてあげようかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I get you expelled, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't do th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことできるわけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.46,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,出来ないと思うのはあんたの自由よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just keep telling yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:37.67,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お騒がせして　すみませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A rich girl who abuses her influence\Nto crush underfoot all who defy her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:44.76,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,権力を盾にはむかう者を叩き潰すお嬢様
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.86,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まるっきり悪役だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a total villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,手っ取り早く解決できたんだからいいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of her quick, so what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I missed Kaoru-{\i1}chan{\i} in\Nher bunny ears and white bikini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.04,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,薫ちゃんのウサギ耳白ビギニが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you resort to threats to run her off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか早くゲームをやりたくてあの人を追い払ったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,just so you could get back to your game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,脅しまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.30,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あったりまえじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sena-{\i1}anego's{\i} principles are unwavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:01.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,星奈の姉御は揺るぎないですね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, if flaunting a little power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:06.51,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,権力をちらつかせるだけでどうにかなる相手なんてどうでもいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to get rid of her,\Nshe's not worth my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with an actual spine\Nwould ignore it and keep coming at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:10.81,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に骨のあるやつはそんなのおかまいなしに向かってくるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little bad for Yusa, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,遊佐には少し悪いことをしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With these two around, the\NNeighbors Club is safe from any challengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.16,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この二人がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.96,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が来ても隣人部は安泰だな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Kodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.29,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば　小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This came up while I was\Non the phone with Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.43,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきパパと電話した時に話題になったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, dear!\N- Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Marry me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたやっぱりあたしと結婚しなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it\Never since the betrothal thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.37,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この間からずっと考えてたんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said this before: I don't care\Nabout some promise between our fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.27,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前にも言ったじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:45.02,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,パパとあんたのお父さんとの約束なんてどうでもいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's that {\i1}promise{\i} that I don't care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:50.25,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でもこの「どうでもいい」ってのは　約束それ自体のことで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When we discovered the engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.82,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか婚約が発覚した時は 結婚そのものがなしみたいになっちゃったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the wedding itself ended up\Ncalled off, but this is a separate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.64,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それとは関係なしに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:00.42,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今のあたしの気持ち的には　あんたと結婚したいと思うのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings right now\Nare that I want to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:01.68,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だってあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I love you and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹のことが好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?! What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you made me screw up, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　ミスしちゃったじゃない　馬鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, sorry. So, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.58,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すまん　何だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.66,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だってじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"What did you say," my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I-I guess I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:22.12,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか　言っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay. I was\Nplanning to tell you sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.62,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいいか　どうせそのうち言うつもりだったし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:33.83,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,えっとね　つまり　何か そういうことだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the deal, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the deal with what?\NThe game was so loud, I couldn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.99,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何が「そういうことなんだ」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.72,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームの音が大きくて　何も聞こえなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.56,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,小鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just remembered something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.44,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば　急用思い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.27,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,光ったはずの星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:34.29,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A stray cloud blocks my view{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:39.80,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of the star I know should be shining there{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:37.49,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,迷った雲が邪魔して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:39.59,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:43.29,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I believe in?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:42.88,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何を信じたらいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:47.14,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was on my way to breaking{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:47.30,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定すぎる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:52.98,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The treasure bred in this all too changeable world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.40,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,育った宝物壊しかけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:57.08,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I was afraid of losing it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:55.97,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なくすのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:58.79,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,不条理だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:00.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those days of sighing "This is absurd"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:00.11,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ため息つき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:03.46,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにかどうで足掻いてた日々
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.38,0:23:03.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And flailing inside my birdcage{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:09.79,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were gazing up at the same sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:07.87,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じ空を見上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.80,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:16.13,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I gripped your hand,{\i}\N{\i1}you gripped back, didn't you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:13.12,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,君の手を握った時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:16.31,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,握り返してくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:22.67,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These joined hands are stronger than any wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:19.45,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,繋がったこの手は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:22.92,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな羽より強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:29.25,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can fly higher even without wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:26.07,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,翼だってなくったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:29.36,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと高く飛べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:32.62,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I know we'll be okay trying now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:32.60,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと今なら大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:38.35,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's grab the stars twinkling in the sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:37.72,夏雪op日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大空輝く星を掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon Astaroth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.50,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,魔人アシタロス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day I'll use the\Nmagic passed on to me by my teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠から受け継いだこの魔法で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日こそあなたを完全に滅ぼす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to destroy you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got spirit, Guernica.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:50.36,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,威勢がいいの　ゲルニカよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But first let me tell\Nyou this: I am your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だがその前に教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:55.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,実はわしは　お前の父だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A horse like you?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:57.94,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてあなたのような　馬が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:23:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:23:59.57,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,話せば長くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:00.24,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあいいです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Just one thing, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:01.97,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ま　待って　では一つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:10.65,Default - Style 13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an8\pos(640,336)}"{\c&H8728E4&}I {\c&HFFFFFF&}______ {\c&H10E5B0&}Many Friends{\c&HFFFFFF&}"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, the final episode of\NHaganai Next: "I ______ Many Friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:02.63,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:05.19,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,はがないネクスト最終話　「僕は友達が…」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shatter the very soul of\Nmy enemy! Nine Lives Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:06.78,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,魂ごと打ち砕け
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:08.95,夏雪日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ナインダイブスブレイカー
